155
00:08:11,910 --> 00:08:12,910
I really am the murderer.

156
00:08:12,910 --> 00:08:14,520
I am the murderer.

157
00:08:14,520 --> 00:08:15,560
I don't know what your family

158
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:16,930
would think if they knew

159
00:08:17,360 --> 00:08:18,200
what you did.

160
00:08:18,840 --> 00:08:20,210
But if I were your daughter,

161
00:08:21,600 --> 00:08:23,050
