166
00:08:48,790 --> 00:08:49,950
I really am the murderer.

167
00:08:49,950 --> 00:08:51,170
I am the murderer.

168
00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:57,450
Since the whole thing

169
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,170
started from this stage,

170
00:08:59,760 --> 00:09:01,570
ending it here

171
00:09:02,240 --> 00:09:03,860
