172
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:05,330
What exactly are you trying to say?

173
00:09:05,840 --> 00:09:06,680
Don't rush.

174
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:09,540
We will definitely catch
the right person.

175
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:11,600
Now,

176
00:09:12,240 --> 00:09:14,410
