233
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,360
If Commander Lei holds him accountable,

234
00:11:31,360 --> 00:11:32,410
Chen Shouting

235
00:11:32,520 --> 00:11:33,740
will not be able to escape.

236
00:11:35,190 --> 00:11:37,020
This way, I can escape from him,

237
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:39,330
and you can take control
of the Chunshou Troupe.

238
00:11:41,520 --> 00:11:43,330
Didn't he already sign the document?

239
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,330
If anything happens to him,

240
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:48,450
you will take over the Chunshou Troupe.

241
00:11:49,880 --> 00:11:51,690
This way, you, I, and Xiaohe

242
00:11:52,000 --> 00:11:53,500
